data.description: Located on the banks of Mattox Creek, this spacious waterfront home offers more than 4000 SF of comfortable living space and   160' of rip-rapped shoreline with private dock. The open floor plan showcases amazing water views and the large deck, patio and screened porch are perfect for relaxing or entertaining. Partially finished basement includes family room, game room, workshop & ample storage.
